WEBVTT

00:07.959 --> 00:09.309
<i>My name is Melinda Gordon.</i>

00:12.030 --> 00:13.030
<i>I just got married,</i>

00:13.169 --> 00:14.559
<i>just moved to a small town,</i>

00:14.693 --> 00:16.294
<i>just opened up an antique shop.</i>

00:16.860 --> 00:18.160
<i>I might be just like you.</i>

00:19.674 --> 00:21.568
<i>Except from the time that I was a little girl,</i>

00:21.569 --> 00:23.469
<i>I knew that I could talk to the dead.</i>

00:24.941 --> 00:26.091
<i>It's all right, honey.</i>

00:26.113 --> 00:28.513
<i>Earthbound spirits, my grandmother called them,</i>

00:28.543 --> 00:32.110
<i>the ones who have not crossed over because they have unfinished business with the living,</i>

00:32.110 --> 00:33.612
<i>and they come to me for help.</i>

00:35.040 --> 00:36.143
<i>To tell you my story,</i>

00:36.663 --> 00:38.017
<i>I have to tell you theirs.</i>

00:42.532 --> 00:43.684
So today,

00:43.934 --> 00:47.637
25 years after judge Walter Merrick took his oath of office,

00:48.352 --> 00:51.002
we are here to dedicate this courthouse in his name.

00:52.222 --> 00:56.122
These qualities have earned him the deep respect which he so richly deserves.

00:57.741 --> 00:59.559
So how come I've never heard of this guy?

00:59.560 --> 01:01.660
Maybe you need to be on trial more often.

01:02.498 --> 01:03.870
- You're hilarious.
- Yeah.

01:04.455 --> 01:07.400
Fair, impartial, and open-minded,

01:08.377 --> 01:10.185
a man of learning and knowledge--

01:14.382 --> 01:18.364
I've seen his name in the paper a few times. He gives lots of money to local charities.

01:18.365 --> 01:20.765
And now I'd like all of you to stand with me...

01:21.300 --> 01:22.800
On this momentous occasion...

01:25.341 --> 01:27.431
as we honor this great man.

